Tavatron growled softly, she didn't like this. It was too easy. Did 
Prowl really think the Alliance would just let them walk out of here? 
However, if the Alliance did allow them safe passage thorugh their 
ship, it only proves just how gullible they are. Tavatron sighed, for 
now she may as well go along with it. 

Tavatron sheathed her sword, taking one last look over her shoulder
at Dinobot, motioning for him to follow. Tavatron then turned so that
her optics faced directly forward, making sure not to make eye
contact with any Alliance members. Tavatron followed closely behind 
Iron Raptor as she exited the torture chamber and entered the hallway.
